dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of 44 competitive collegiate distance runners from the NCAA Pac-12 conference, including 114 collections of running data at multiple speeds. The dataset features ground reaction force (GRF) data collected at 1,000 Hz from instrumented treadmills and acceleration and angular velocity data from wearable IMU sensors at 500 Hz.
dcterms:title: Pac-12 Dataset
